Available Tools: open_garage | close_garage | get_garage_status | set_garage_timer
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "door_id": "string", "delay_seconds": number }
Response Schema: { "door_id": "string", "state": "open|closed|opening|closing", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Can you tell me if the east wing garage is open right now?
Call: { "func_call": "get_garage_status", "door_id": "garage_east_05", "delay_seconds": 0 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_east_05", "state": "open", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T09:15:30Z" }

Question: Please program the north gate to shut automatically in 8 minutes.
Call: { "func_call": "set_garage_timer", "door_id": "garage_north_06", "delay_seconds": 480 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_north_06", "state": "open", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T09:18:45Z" }

Question: I need to know the current position of the barn door immediately.
Call: { "func_call": "get_garage_status", "door_id": "garage_barn_07", "delay_seconds": 0 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_barn_07", "state": "closing", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T09:22:10Z" }

Question: Set a timer so the east wing door closes in 12 minutes.
Call: { "func_call": "set_garage_timer", "door_id": "garage_east_05", "delay_seconds": 720 }
Response: { "door_id": "garage_east_05", "state": "open", "timestamp": "2023-11-02T09:30:00Z" }

